These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Birthday   | december | july | august | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, baseball, swimming, badminton
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | baseball | climbing | badminton | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
House: ranch-style, wooden, farmhouse, cottage
1. the wooden house is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the cottage house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| House   | ranch-style | farmhouse | wooden | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
