.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, blues, disco, salsa
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | country | disco | blues | salsa |

