.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, green, light-blue, apricot
1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
4. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Color   | light-blue | green | yellow | apricot |

