3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Sport   | cricket | ice-hockey | badminton | rugby |

