3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Sport   | parkour | cricket | surfing | cycling |

