.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, romance, sports
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching sports movies##2
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |   3   |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | romance | sports | mystery |

