.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-16::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, billiard, go
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2  |      3       |   4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | go | bridge | billiard |

