.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
House: gothic-revival, victorian, modern, farmhouse
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
4. the victorian house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| House   | modern | victorian | gothic-revival | farmhouse |

 